node.text: Cheers to having ladies in my courses that are crushing it out there on deck & are fellow 200 ton Captains! 🙌⚓️ #girlbosses #crushingit #ladiesondeck #yachting #keepadvancing

Photo shared by Malia White on August 14, 2021 tagging @nadinerajabi, @katiefloody, @courtneyveale, @captainsandrayawn, @mathewshea, @zeedempers, @lloydbelowdeck, and @davidpascoe91. May be an image of 1 person, standing, screen, camera, french fries, television and text.

node.text: That’s a wrap! Hope everyone is enjoying this season of #belowdeckmed! There’s still a lot of excitement to come! I have to say this was the most fun I’ve had filming a season, thanks to the boat & production crew. A lot of work goes into making this show what it is and I’m grateful to be a part of it! ⚓️❤️ #belowdeck #greenscreen #thatsawrap #yachting #tv @bravotv
